/******************************************************************************                      
** Name		 : USP_PP_GetValidationEngineBeneficiaryPaymentCondition                      
** Short Desc: To get Payment Condition Status
**                      
** Full Description: To get Payment Condition Status for Beneficiary Payment/PGCalcImport Payment Type          
**        
**                              
** Input Arguments: 
	 @UserID INT,
	 @Type Bit =1--auto 

**         
** Sample Call     

EXEC USP_PP_GetValidationEngineBeneficiaryPaymentCondition 1       

                 	
